data.description: Gorgeous newly built 3 Bed/2.5 Bath two-story "move-in ready" home (2022) housed on a premium lot with a long driveway and greenway views. This beautiful home features an open floor plan with 9-ft. ceilings and a huge great room with tons of natural light. Spacious kitchen with 42-in. upper cabinets is complimented by beautiful granite countertops, breakfast bar, striking tile backsplash, farmhouse sink, pantry and stainless steel appliances. Convenient half bath/powder room on main level. The private Owner’s Suite is secluded behind French doors which boasts a huge bedroom connected to an ensuite bathroom that has double Silestone® vanities.  Owner’s Suite has a walk-in closet along with cabinet and linen storage, tub/shower combination with tile surround. Upstairs loft bonus space is ideal for an office/gaming/media or play room.  Two additional bedrooms and full bath are on the opposite end of the home.  Plush carpet in the loft area and bedrooms, Sherwin-Williams® interior paint and Moen® faucets throughout the home.  Generous pantry, closet and cabinet space as well as under stair storage.  Luxury vinyl wood tile flooring throughout the home.  Designated laundry room.  Built in pest control system. Smart thermostat. Wired for fiber optics and security systems.  Water Softener.  Spacious backyard with extended patio, no rear facing neighbors and a greenway view.  A property not to be missed!
